Package utils

Class Function1V

java.lang.Object
utils.Dataset
utils.Curve
utils.Function1V
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Function
public class Function1V extends Curve implements Function
A functional interface that is open for use. It uses derivative algorithm to explore a single variable function with a constant plot density, and stores the data into a matrix.
Author:
Yuelong Li
